Original repository: https://github.com/leggedrobotics/rsl_rl

## Modifications and Enhancements

This fork includes the following major modifications and enhancements by 
Shanghai Jiao Tong University, MVASL Lab:

- RSL RL MM Series Interface for multi-modal imitation learning
- Enhanced environment interface with reference observation support
- Student-teacher transformer architectures
- Multi-modal PPO implementation
- Distillation algorithms for knowledge transfer
- Integration with GBC (Gradient-Based Control) project

All modifications are licensed under the same BSD-3-Clause license terms as 
stated above.
